# ============================================================

# ✅ 14. Explicitly Allow Safe Portfolio Evidence

# ============================================================

# Allow redacted screenshot evidence.

!01-web-vapt/screenshots/*.png
!02-api-security/screenshots/*.png
!03-ad-network/screenshots/*.png
!04-cloud-security/screenshots/*.png
!05-azure-security/screenshots/*.png

# Allow Markdown documentation.

!README.md
!**/README.md
!06-roadmap/certification-roadmap.md

# Allow empty folder placeholders.

!.gitkeep
!**/.gitkeep

# Allow sanitized Postman collections.

!02-api-security/postman-collections/*.postman_collection.json
